# std/os deterministic helpers

```scalascript
[envOrElse, pathJoin, pathBasename, pathExtname](std/os.ssc)

println(envOrElse("SCALASCRIPT_CONFORMANCE_ENV_THAT_SHOULD_NOT_EXIST", "fallback"))

val joined = pathJoin("/usr", "local", "bin", "ssc")
println(joined)
println(pathBasename(joined))
println(pathExtname("/docs/readme.md"))
```
